title: Nigel Farage – 2022 Comments on Rishi Sunak
author: admin
summary: The comments made by Nigel Farage, the former Leader of UKIP, on Twitter on 23 October 2022.
content:
Rishi Sunak will not hold the Red Wall. Labour will be pleased.
